{
  "texts": [
    "We found that RECTIFIER can accurately screen patients for clinical trials using an actively enrolling heart failure clinical trial as an example.",
    "In specific aspects, RECTIFIER performance for clinical trial screening surpassed traditional methods with study staff.",
    "Furthermore, the cost of using RECTIFIER was only 10 cents per patient.",
    "We believe these findings can lead to substantial improvements in the efficiency of patient recruitment for clinical trials.",
    "We found that both sensitivity and specificity of RECTIFIER was high, while study staff had slightly lower sensitivity and significantly lower specificity."
  ]
}